DynamicGlycosylationSimulator package

This package contains the simulation modules for dynamic N-linked Glycosylation simulation.

Submodules

DynamicGlycosylationSimulator.CellCultureDerivative.cell_culture_derivative(z, y, p, fp, feed)[source]

Solve the dynamic glycosylation model between two samplings

Parameters

  • z (array) – time interval between two samplings

  • y (array) – perfusion cell culture state

  • p (GlycosylationModelParamClass) – N-linked glycosylation model parameters

  • fp (GlycosylationNetwork) – N-linked glycosylation network

  • feed (array) – feeding conditions between two samplings

Returns ndarray

updated cell culture states [volume, VCD, Mn, Amm, mAb, Galactose] and 33 oligsaccharides

DynamicGlycosylationSimulator.DynamicGlycosylationSolver module

class DynamicGlycosylationSimulator.DynamicGlycosylationSolver.DynamicGlycosylationSolver(initial_states, feed_profile, p, fp, dt, total_time=None)[source]

Bases: object

Class for solving the dynamic N-linked Glycosylation model

Parameters

  • initial_states (ndarray) – initial proess state

  • feed_profile (ndarray) – feed strategy including Time [min], Fin/Volume, Bleed blend [%], Mn in feed [uM], Galactose in feed [mM]

  • p (GlycosylationModelParamClass) – N-linked glycosylation model parameters

  • fp (GlycosylationNetwork) – N-linked glycosylation network

  • dt (int) – sampling time [min]

  • total_time (int) – total run time [min]

Return array deriv

derivatives of N-linked glycosylation models

DynamicGlycosylationSimulator.InnerFunction module

DynamicGlycosylationSimulator.InnerFunction.innerFunction(x, p, fp, t_span, feed_cond, ic_states, ic_macro_rest)[source]

Solve the dynamic glycosylation model between two samplings

Parameters

  • x (CellCultureVariables) – perfusion cell culture related data (ammonium, Manganese chloride and Nucleotide sugar in cytosol)

  • p (GlycosylationModelParamClass) – N-linked glycosylation model parameters

  • fp (GlycosylationNetwork) – N-linked glycosylation network

  • t_span (int) – sampling time [min]

  • feed_cond (ndarray) – feeding conditions between two samplings

  • ic_states (array) – initial state including volume, VCD*V, manganese*V, ammonia*V, mab*V, Gal*V

  • ic_macro_rest (array) – 33 oligsaccharides

Returns ndarray

updated cell culture states [volume, VCD, Mn, Amm, mAb, Galactose] and 33 oligsaccharides

Solve the dynamic glycosylation model between two samplings

Parameters

  • mult (array) – updated parameters for the perfusion cell culture and the N-glycosylation model from MIT

  • p (GlycosylationModelParamClass) – N-linked glycosylation model parameters

  • fp (GlycosylationNetwork) – N-linked glycosylation network

  • t_span (int) – sampling time [min]

  • feed_cond (ndarray) – feeding conditions between two samplings

  • ic_states (array) – initial state including volume, VCD*V, manganese*V, ammonia*V, mab*V, Gal*V

  • ic_macro_rest (array) – 33 oligsaccharides

Returns ndarray

updated cell culture states (i.e. volume, VCD, Mn, Amm, mAb, Galactose) and 33 oligsaccharides
